ry Glen Ross","video":false,"overview":"Times are tough at Premiere Properties. Shelley \"the machine\" Levene and Dave Moss are veteran salesmen, but only Ricky Roma is on a hot streak. The new Glengarry sales leads could turn everything around, but the front office is holding them back until these \"losers\" prove themselves. Then someone decides to take matters into his own hands, stealing the Glengarry leads and leaving everyone wondering who did it.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":2.3511,"vote_count":1554,"poster_path":"/zcaEDx8KlVfh4vKfMNLhiSi5Oz4.jpg","release_date":"1992-09-10","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/qukaw3P4MOFNdxjhNpClhT9unr8.jpg","original_title":"Glengarry Glen Ross","original_language":"en"},{"id":1262426,"adult":false,"title":"Tinā","video":false,"overview":"A woman grieving her daughter's death in the Christchurch earthquakes, becomes a substitute teacher at an elite private school. Unexpectedly, she discovers students lacking guidance and care, prompting her to provide inspiration and support.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":3.2148,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/nx9DPAzainWTqPKuirLIXasbU3z.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-27","vote_average":8.1,"backdrop_path":"/e4anpBBWKiGVfleKSicuXxcrGiY.jpg","original_title":"Tinā","original_language":"en"},{"id":1059007,"adult":false,"title":"Agra","video":false,"overview":"The story of a family and an exploration of space in an increasingly crowded world. It follows the quest for a sexual odyssey of an individual.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":3.3344,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/biX8D3kSh4HuZzf1r0ynRgaEJte.jpg","release_date":"2025-11-14","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/A8tmOkIdD9Uban7JjYQUDuXv6kP.jpg","original_title":"Agra","original_language":"hi"},{"id":2065,"adult":false,"title":"Could This Be Love?","video":false,"overview":"Lucas, a wealthy, 43 year-old divorced businessman, is irresistibly attracted to Elsa, a 38 year old renowned sculptor from whom he has commissioned a piece t